name: Aid For Japan Charity Poster
description:
In light of the tragedy that has befallen Japan, I've come up with a poster with 100% of all profits going towards the UNICEF Earthquake Relief Fund. For only $20.00, you can join my effort and lend a helping hand to those affected by the disaster. 

The fantastically generous screenprinters at Fleaheart of Brooklyn have selflessly offered to donate all setup and printing costs.

16 x 24 screenprint on 140# French Paper, Madero Beach Speckletone. Signed and numbered edition of 100.

Please allow up to two weeks for delivery.

name: La Ruine de L'Homme
